ery day Muslims obey Allah a celebration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 1, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Rajab reported: Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cEvery day in which Allah is not disobeyed is a celebration. Every day the believer spends in obedience, servitude, remembrance, and gratitude is a celebration.\u201d Source: Lat\u0323a\u0304'if al-Ma'a\u0304rif 1\/278 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0631\u062c\u0628 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0633\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0635\u0631\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u062a\u0639\u0627\u0644\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36091,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/11\/hasan-taqabbal-allahu-minna\/","url_meta":{"origin":36167,"position":1},"title":"Hasan on Eid: May Allah accept from us and from you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hawshab ibn \u2018Aqil reported: I met Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, on the day of Eid and I said, \u201cMay Allah accept good deeds from us and from you.\u201d Al-Hasan said, \u201cYes, may Allah accept good deeds from us and from you.\u201d Source: al-Du\u2019a\u0304\u2019 li-T\u0323abara\u0304ni 930 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19324,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonli